      "scene": "S1-02"
    },
    {
      "zh": "工资到账，",
      "en": "Your paycheck lands,",
      "scene": "S1-03"
    },
    {
      "zh": "第一反应不是松一口气，",
      "en": "and your first reaction isn't relief,",
      "scene": "S1-03"
    },
    {
      "zh": "是打开计算器，",
