      "scene": "S1-04"
    },
    {
      "zh": "算完发现，",
      "en": "When you're done you realize,",
      "scene": "S1-05"
    },
    {
      "zh": "这份工作你再不情愿，",
      "en": "no matter how unwilling you are at this job,",
      "scene": "S1-05"
    },
    {
      "zh": "也得撑下去。",
      "en": "you have to keep going.",
      "scene": "S1-05"
    },
    {
      "zh": "二十岁那会儿，",
      "en": "Back when you were twenty,",
      "scene": "S1-06"
    },
    {
      "zh": "你觉得时间多得是，",
      "en": "you thought you had all the time in the world,",
      "scene": "S1-06"
    },
    {
      "zh": "犯错没事，",
      "en": "mistakes were fine,",
      "scene": "S1-07"
    },
    {
      "zh": "回头再来。",
      "en": "you could always start over.",
      "scene": "S1-07"
    },
    {
      "zh": "三十岁那年，",
      "en": "At thirty,",
      "scene": "S1-08"
    },
    {
      "zh": "账单和房贷",
      "en": "the bills and the mortgage",
      "scene": "S1-08"
    },
    {
      "zh": "已经替你做了一半的决定。",
      "en": "had already made half your decisions for you.",
      "scene": "S1-08"
    },
    {
      "zh": "到了四十岁，",
      "en": "By forty,",
      "scene": "S1-09"
    },
    {
      "zh": "你坐在工位上盯着屏幕，",
      "en": "you sit at your desk staring at the screen,",
      "scene": "S1-09"
    },
    {
      "zh": "心里很清楚——",
      "en": "and you know it in your bones——",
      "scene": "S1-10"
    },
    {
      "zh": "你已经付不起试错的成本了。",
      "en": "you can't afford the cost of getting it wrong anymore.",
      "scene": "S1-10"
    },
    {
      "zh": "可越是付不起，",
      "en": "Yet the more you can't afford it,",
      "scene": "S1-11"
    },
    {
      "zh": "你越是站在原地不动。",
      "en": "the more you stand still.",
      "scene": "S1-11"
    },
    {
      "zh": "你不是没看见身边那些人。",
      "en": "It's not like you haven't seen the people around you.",
      "scene": "S1-12"
    },
    {
      "zh": "那个天天说要辞职的同事，",
      "en": "The coworker who says he'll quit every single day,",
      "scene": "S1-12"
    },
    {
      "zh": "三年了还在原位置。",
      "en": "three years on, still in the same seat.",
      "scene": "S1-12"
    },
    {
      "zh": "那个早就睡不好的发小，",
      "en": "The childhood friend who long stopped sleeping well,",
      "scene": "S1-13"
    },
    {
      "zh": "每天熬到两点，",
      "en": "stays up until two every night,",
      "scene": "S1-13"
    },
    {
      "zh": "第二天照样上班。",
      "en": "and shows up to work the next morning all the same.",
      "scene": "S1-13"
    },
    {
      "zh": "那个把大好十年",
      "en": "The one who burned his best ten years",
      "scene": "S1-14"
    },
    {
      "zh": "耗在一个错方向上的人，",
      "en": "on the wrong direction——",
      "scene": "S1-14"
    },
    {
      "zh": "你心里有个数，",
      "en": "you know in your gut,",
      "scene": "S1-15"
    },
    {
      "zh": "那也可能是你。",
      "en": "that could be you too.",
      "scene": "S1-15"
    },
    {
      "zh": "这十年，",
      "en": "This decade,",
      "scene": "S1-16"
    },
    {
      "zh": "你走的每一步，",
      "en": "every step you take,",
      "scene": "S1-16"
    },
    {
      "zh": "都在替你五十岁以后的自己签字。",
      "en": "is signing the contract for the you that comes after fifty.",
      "scene": "S1-16"
    },
    {
      "zh": "你翻来覆去想的，",
      "en": "What you keep turning over in your head,",
      "scene": "S1-17"
    },
    {
      "zh": "其实就是几件事。",
      "en": "is really just a few questions.",
      "scene": "S1-17"
    },
    {
      "zh": "要靠什么吃饭，",
      "en": "What will you live on,",
      "scene": "S1-18"
    },
    {
      "zh": "路要怎么走，",
      "en": "how do you walk the road,",
      "scene": "S1-18"
    },
    {
      "zh": "万一走错了又怎么办。",
      "en": "and what if you take the wrong turn.",
      "scene": "S1-18"
    },
    {
      "zh": "先说靠什么吃饭。",
      "en": "Start with what you live on.",
      "scene": "S1-19"
    },
    {
      "zh": "你愿不愿意，",
      "en": "Are you willing,",
      "scene": "S1-19"
    },
    {
      "zh": "再过十年",
      "en": "ten years from now,",
      "scene": "S1-20"
    },
    {
      "zh": "还是靠这副身子骨换钱。",
      "en": "to still be trading this body for money.",
      "scene": "S1-20"
    },
    {
      "zh": "三十五岁以后体力是往下走的，",
      "en": "After thirty-five, physical strength only goes down,",
      "scene": "S1-21"
    },
    {
      "zh": "可你这些年攒下的阅历和判断",
      "en": "but the experience and judgment you've built up",
      "scene": "S1-21"
    },
    {
      "zh": "才刚刚开始值钱。",
      "en": "are only just starting to be worth something.",
      "scene": "S1-21"
    },
    {
      "zh": "光靠力气的那条路",
      "en": "The road built on muscle alone",
      "scene": "S1-22"
    },
    {
      "zh": "只会越走越窄，",
      "en": "only gets narrower the further you walk,",
      "scene": "S1-22"
    },
    {
      "zh": "总有一天你干不动了，",
      "en": "and one day you simply can't keep up,",
      "scene": "S1-23"
    },
    {
      "zh": "路就把你扔下了。",
      "en": "and the road throws you off.",
      "scene": "S1-23"
    },
    {
      "zh": "至于怎么走，",
      "en": "As for how to walk it,",
      "scene": "S1-24"
    },
    {
      "zh": "不是坐在沙发上想出来的。",
      "en": "you don't figure that out on the couch.",
      "scene": "S1-24"
    },
    {
      "zh": "是小步走，",
      "en": "You walk in small steps,",
      "scene": "S1-25"
    },
    {
      "zh": "走错了回头，",
      "en": "turn back when you're wrong,",
      "scene": "S1-25"
    },
    {
      "zh": "走对了再往前一点。",
      "en": "push a bit further when you're right.",
      "scene": "S1-25"
    },
    {
      "zh": "你之前怕的不是试错，",
      "en": "What you used to fear wasn't the trial and error,",
      "scene": "S1-26"
    },
    {
      "zh": "是怕周围人看你失败的眼神。",
      "en": "it was the eyes around you watching you fail.",
      "scene": "S1-26"
    },
    {
      "zh": "可那些眼神，",
      "en": "But those eyes,",
      "scene": "S1-27"
    },
    {
      "zh": "三个月就忘了，",
      "en": "they forget in three months,",
      "scene": "S1-27"
    },
    {
      "zh": "你浪费的时间",
      "en": "while the time you wasted",
      "scene": "S1-28"
    },
    {
      "zh": "却永远要不回来。",
      "en": "you can never take back.",
      "scene": "S1-28"
    },
    {
      "zh": "那万一走错了——掉头。",
      "en": "And if you do take the wrong turn—— turn around.",
      "scene": "S1-29"
    },
    {
      "zh": "不是再撑一下，",
      "en": "Not hang on a little longer,",
      "scene": "S1-30"
    },
    {
      "zh": "不是再等一等，",
      "en": "not wait it out a little more,",
      "scene": "S1-30"
    },
    {
      "zh": "不是再咬咬牙。",
      "en": "not grit your teeth one more time.",
      "scene": "S1-31"
    },
    {
      "zh": "是掉头。",
      "en": "Turn around.",
      "scene": "S1-31"
    },
    {
      "zh": "人到中年，",
      "en": "In middle age,",
      "scene": "S1-32"
    },
    {
      "zh": "最贵的从来不是钱，",
      "en": "the most expensive thing has never been money,",
      "scene": "S1-32"
    },
    {
      "zh": "是那段你已经耗进去、",
      "en": "it's the stretch of time you've already poured in",
      "scene": "S1-33"
    },
    {
      "zh": "再也要不回来的时间。",
      "en": "and can never get back.",
      "scene": "S1-33"
    },
    {
      "zh": "承认走错，",
      "en": "Admitting you were wrong",
      "scene": "S1-34"
    },
    {
      "zh": "比死撑下去要勇敢得多。",
      "en": "takes far more courage than holding on.",
      "scene": "S1-34"
    },
    {
      "zh": "能掉头的人，",
      "en": "Only those who can turn around",
      "scene": "S1-35"
    },
    {
      "zh": "才走得到后面。",
      "en": "make it all the way through.",
      "scene": "S1-35"
    },
    {
      "zh": "我见过很多人，",
      "en": "I've seen many people,",
      "scene": "S1-36"
    },
    {
      "zh": "四十岁还在为一个错决定续命，",
      "en": "at forty still keeping a wrong decision on life support,",
      "scene": "S1-36"
    },
    {
      "zh": "理由是“都走到这一步了”。",
      "en": "and the reason is, “I've already come this far.”",
      "scene": "S1-37"
    },
    {
      "zh": "可这一步以后还有更长的路，",
      "en": "But there's a much longer road after this step,",
      "scene": "S1-38"
    },
    {
      "zh": "你把脚埋在错的地里，",
      "en": "and if you bury your feet in the wrong soil,",
      "scene": "S1-38"
    },
    {
      "zh": "它不会自己长出对的花。",
      "en": "it won't grow the right flowers on its own.",
      "scene": "S1-38"
    },
    {
      "zh": "你不需要别人替你拍板。",
      "en": "You don't need someone else to make the call for you.",
      "scene": "S1-39"
    },
    {
      "zh": "你只需要在今晚躺下之前，",
      "en": "You only need, before you lie down tonight,",
      "scene": "S1-39"
    },
    {
      "zh": "问自己一句：",
      "en": "to ask yourself one thing:",
      "scene": "S1-39"
    },
    {
      "zh": "明天醒来，",
      "en": "when I wake up tomorrow,",
      "scene": "S1-40"
    },
    {
      "zh": "我还要不要在这条路上",
      "en": "do I still want to be on this road,",
      "scene": "S1-40"
    },
    {
      "zh": "再耗一年。",
      "en": "for another year.",
      "scene": "S1-40"
    },
    {
      "zh": "如果答案不是肯定的，",
      "en": "If the answer isn't yes,",
      "scene": "S1-41"
    },
    {
      "zh": "那就别等下一个十年，",
      "en": "then don't wait another decade,",
      "scene": "S1-41"
    },
    {
      "zh": "再来后悔今晚的沉默。",
      "en": "to regret your silence tonight.",
      "scene": "S1-41"
    }
